code: @Before public void setUp() throws Exception {     RouterFunction<?> route = route(GET("/test"), request -> ServerResponse.ok().syncBody("It works!")).     this.testClient = WebTestClient.bindToRouterFunction(route).build(). }
@Test public void test() throws Exception {     this.testClient.get().uri("/test").exchange().expectStatus().isOk().expectBody(String.class).isEqualTo("It works!"). }
